td.div: English: Logo for Bluesky, a social platform. The butterfly logo originally premiered in December 2023, replacing a photo of clouds in a blue sky. This version of the logo is an update from the previous logo, lowering the focal convergence point of the four wings, and fixing symmetry between the wings.
